{"tid":2329505,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中聯辦設8「紫荊」新公司  紫荊黨成立前兩周出現惹關注","createTime":"2020-12-17T09:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:42:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b28d7607a436477c8f86157cd267f70fc2a28697","tid":2329505,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/374HTHJS6NAK5IJT3AXH4P5BWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F374HTHJS6NAK5IJT3AXH4P5BWM%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28cZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=6fc27b87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F374HTHJS6NAK5IJT3AXH4P5BWM%2F&h=a8d0ea79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/374HTHJS6NAK5IJT3AXH4P5BWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦設8「紫荊」新公司 <br />\n紫荊黨成立前兩周出現惹關注<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/x919QChqkHMW0BSWsW7gk9r74Ak=/1000x611/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MJN3CVYRBVETNFG756YCG4AETE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fx919QChqkHMW0BSWsW7gk9r74Ak%3D%2F1000x611%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMJN3CVYRBVETNFG756YCG4AETE.jpg&h=2b4884c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■本報登門訪問紫荊養生公司，惟女職員不作任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年5月成立的「紫荊黨」近日高調宣傳，本報發現紫荊黨成立前約兩星期，有八間以「紫荊」為首的新公司成立，兩位董事報住地址，均為中聯辦及關聯公司新民置業名下物業。近日中央加強對港管治，這些新公司與紫荊黨「前後腳」成立，引起外界關注，有分析認為雖然未有直接證據指紫荊黨與中聯辦的關係，但相信紫荊黨不能避過共產黨的控制。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：多商界出身 紫荊黨威脅建制派<br />\n<br />\n公司註冊處資料顯示，有八間公司今年4月27日成立，名稱以「紫荊」為首，包含紫荊展覽、紫荊出版、紫荊養生及紫荊健康文化等。董事為王耀輝及張麗新，分別報住霎西街5號及鉑峯單位，前者業主為新民置業有限公司，鉑峯所有單位業主均為中聯辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KjgpqiKqZXrUosrc3qVoJjGUCRw=/1029x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJTQ2JAWN5FYXA4UQIGWPSHMGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKjgpqiKqZXrUosrc3qVoJjGUCRw%3D%2F1029x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJTQ2JAWN5FYXA4UQIGWPSHMGU.jpg&h=122d7dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紫荊黨主席李山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女職員聞採訪即關門<br />\n<br />\n新民置業董事及股東均為中聯辦員工，中聯辦去年曾指出，公司有關物業用作員工辦公和住宿。這些紫荊公司的辦公室地址為信德中心西座10樓一個單位，亦是新民置業名下物業。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨到信德中心上址單位，見門外上掛有「紫荊雜誌社」及「紫荊研究院」等水牌，單位內辦公室範圍一片漆黑，有。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ka5i_gLj8uisPX6XZ27gEzDqKPI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XIMW2LPKWZE2RPJMN5RPCS65FY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKa5i_gLj8uisPX6XZ27gEzDqKPI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXIMW2LPKWZE2RPJMN5RPCS65FY.jpg&h=4ddef777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中聯辦主任駱惠寧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評論員稱京擬接管港政權<br />\n<br />\n翻查《紫荊》雜誌社編採名單，總編輯楊勇、副社長許俐麗及副總編輯刀書林，分別報住蒲飛路18號、西營盤樂怡軒及柴灣灣景園單位，同樣由新民置業持有。該雜誌由中聯辦透過廣東註冊公司「廣東新文化事業發展」持有，此公司亦持有《文匯報》及《大公報》等左報。近日備受公眾關注的紫荊黨，董事之一李山早前便是首次以黨主席身份，接受《紫荊》網站訪問，大談政策議題。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者致電中聯辦查詢，接聽電話的職員指自己不清楚，記者追問應該致電何人查詢，職員亦未有提供。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員程翔日前於網。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n紫荊黨早於今年5月14日成立，但至。。。。。。。肯定的是，中聯辦欲影響香港各層面的野心已越來越浮面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JVDwjmbGb7LN06mJwDFYxF2sQwg=/1937x896/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/56ZP4XACARBOFDDL7L6MJIUH3Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJVDwjmbGb7LN06mJwDFYxF2sQwg%3D%2F1937x896%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F56ZP4XACARBOFDDL7L6MJIUH3Y.gif&h=5d30c24f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b885b7442ae8